message.content: cs.CR, cs.IT, cs.AR, cs.SE, cs.ET - The paper discusses threats and schemes related to hardware security, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). It also discusses the use of 3D integration to enhance hardware security, which involves aspects of information theory (cs.IT) and computer architecture (cs.AR). The paper also mentions the need for secure system-level integration (cs.SE) and shielding for 3D ICs, which involves aspects of electronic engineering (cs.ET).
